snippet.title: Sword Art Online: Fatal Bullet - Dissonance of the Nexus Expansion Opening Movie | PS4, XB1, PC
snippet.description:
Live the story of Sword Art Online: Fatal Bullet with the Dissonance of Nexus Expansion! Check out the Opening Cinematic trailer and get ready to become the hero once again on January 18th, 2019! 

Pick up Sword Art Online: Fatal Bullet today: https://bandainam.co/SAOFB
